SpanLib - Spectral Analysis Library
===================================

Intent:
-------
Provides a fortran 90 libraries and a python module
to performs analyses such as Principal Component
Analysis and Multichannel Singular Spectrum Analysis.
This packages is suitable for analysis studies of
climate or financial variability.

Authors:
--------
Stephane Raynaud
Charles Doutriaux

Licence:
--------
Lesser GNU Public Licence
See COPYING file

Documentation:
--------------
- On the web: http://spanlib.sourceforge.net/
- One packaged is installed, typically in:
  file://<prefix_dir>/share/spanlib/html

Installation:
-------------
Try ./configure && make && make install (as root)
See INSTALL file


